# Desktop Registry auditing rules (Registry2)
# For: win-registry2.ps1  (Apply to "Subkeys only")
# Format: id|path|perm|note

reg2_portproxy|HKLM:\SYSTEM\CurrentControlSet\Services\PortProxy|SetValue|PortProxy (subkeys only)

# Insider / collection signals (desktop-focused)
reg2_usbstor|HKLM:\SYSTEM\CurrentControlSet\Services\USBSTOR|SetValue,Delete,QueryValues|USB storage usage (subkeys only)
reg2_mic|HKLM:\SOFTWARE\Microsoft\Windows\CurrentVersion\CapabilityAccessManager\ConsentStore\microphone|SetValue|Microphone consent (subkeys)
reg2_webcam|HKLM:\SOFTWARE\Microsoft\Windows\CurrentVersion\CapabilityAccessManager\ConsentStore\webcam|SetValue|Webcam consent (subkeys)
reg2_mic_np|HKLM:\SOFTWARE\Microsoft\Windows\CurrentVersion\CapabilityAccessManager\ConsentStore\microphone\NonPackaged|SetValue|Microphone NonPackaged (subkeys)
reg2_webcam_np|HKLM:\SOFTWARE\Microsoft\Windows\CurrentVersion\CapabilityAccessManager\ConsentStore\webcam\NonPackaged|SetValue|Webcam NonPackaged (subkeys)
